com.legacy.structure_gel.util

Class DimensionTypeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.legacy.structure_gel.util.DimensionTypeBuilder

  • public class DimensionTypeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A way of creating a DimensionType in a builder format. All values are defaulted to what they would be for the overworld.
    Author:
    David
